</p></li><li id="LI_702F99C3DB3C4D4DB50DF6294246FCC4" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the ink system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="02DISA012" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-1C874C66-3A17-4AC4-886B-753A1A37D196.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 02 Open the ink system?>02 Open the ink system</xref> 
</p></li><li id="LI_B00BCB492EC546EE98CD25996779F334" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the rear top cover of the ink system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="02DISA014" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-44A21941-A21F-4C37-A066-3CEA7BE54DAA.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 02 How to remove the rear top cover of the ink system...?>02 How to remove the rear top cover of the ink system</xref> 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the pump tube. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See 
<xref keyref="02DISA026" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-17BE5A1E-1F83-432B-A7C3-6E2D5D312EEC.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 02 How to remove the pump tube of the ink pump?>02 How to remove the pump tube of the ink pump</xref> 
</p></li></ul></prereq><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_44E3E3F07D374BF6964EC50817FE9018" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_52DBF4023EA944F89CD5A1B41DA11017" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Cloth 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T20 
</p></li><li id="LI_929C0F12811B4096BB70DA320BD9C6C8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves: 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex</b> 93-260 gloves. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-6A8315DA-0FC7-4677-9DAB-BA6C38097044" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-B3A08F61-0439-45C1-ABE7-70C25E6CF03A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-CFA7FB5A-B39F-4FC3-8EE9-47341DE8659C-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-CFA7FB5A-B39F-4FC3-8EE9-47341DE8659C-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_02E80458CCD7453CA0EF1FDB3BE8E5D3" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to remove</title><table id="TABLE_D003021DEA3B44B68823500D2EF89AF3" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Disconnect the connector of the ink pump (in between the metal covers). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-E596261F-355E-4145-883E-ABE1BEC3D383" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-81B1BCD3-1686-48A6-8B01-71C6F92711FC-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-81B1BCD3-1686-48A6-8B01-71C6F92711FC-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the screw (T20) of the ink pump assembly. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-6BF9959E-223B-4D49-992D-04B033553C54" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-4DF75BEF-283D-4AD0-9E98-7F23897BDBAB-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4DF75BEF-283D-4AD0-9E98-7F23897BDBAB-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Lift and remove the ink pump assembly. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-CE694895-6AB6-4C52-B64D-30353F69E0E6" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-790AE56A-A778-4C66-A3CD-071E4FFBDDBE-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-790AE56A-A778-4C66-A3CD-071E4FFBDDBE-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Use a screwdriver to unhook the motor from the bracket. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the bracket from the motor. 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-2904CD40-40BC-4005-9BCE-F87F405AFE26" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-36C7865D-6096-4F6A-9F11-38C9EB7B99BE-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-36C7865D-6096-4F6A-9F11-38C9EB7B99BE-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-6CF64F8C-F717-48B1-9BDF-D488E264AF77" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-CFA7FB5A-B39F-4FC3-8EE9-47341DE8659C-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-CFA7FB5A-B39F-4FC3-8EE9-47341DE8659C-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to install</title><table id="GUID-BDB87D50-9E70-4086-AC9E-FA7970C76B0D" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Install in reverse order. 
</p><note id="GUID-ADEEC0B1-B439-4B32-BFDD-816760E8C948" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Position of the pump tube inside the ink pump on the marker. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Reconnect the Service jumper, exit SDS and press 'Restart' on the operator panel. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">In case a 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">new</b> ink pump is installed, reset the operating time of this pump. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> See : 
<xref keyref="SDS02-8-005" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-00D87248-135A-4E83-B9E5-98156A175BE4.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 02-8-005 Operating time ink pump [0.1s] (02M1, 02M3, 02M5, 02M7, 02M50Mxx) [Maintenance Counters]?>02-8-005 Operating time ink pump [0.1s] (02M1, 02M3, 02M5, 02M7, 02M50Mxx) [Maintenance Counters]</xref>. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-1CE85252-F6D3-4421-930B-8AE723FFB49C.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Dis-assembly</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
